#

Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Roasted Vegetables

$18.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

Main CourseHealthyGrilling

Description

Succulent grilled chicken marinated in zesty lemon and herbs, served with a colorful array of roasted vegetables for a healthy, satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breast: 2 pieces
  • Lemon Juice: 1/4 cup
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 teaspoons, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 teaspoons, chopped
  • Garlic Powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Bell Peppers: 1 cup, chopped
  • Zucchini: 1 cup, sliced
  • Red Onion: 1 medium, sliced
  • Asparagus: 1 cup, trimmed
